HEADWORD: Defix
<hw>De*fix"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>defixus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>defigere</ets> to fix; <ets>de-</ets>
+ <ets>figere</ets> to fix.]</ety> <def>To fix; to fasten; to
establish.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧To <xex>defix</xex> their
princely seat . . . in that extreme province.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Hakluyt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
